What are Fractals?
========================================================

<p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: gray; padding: .25em 1em; border-left: solid 5px #96A2B6;">
<em>a natural phenomenon or a mathematical set that exhibits a repeating pattern that displays at every scale</em> -- <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fractal">wikipedia</a>
</p>

- latin  _frāctus_ -- broken, fractured
- expanding/evolving symmetry
- _"beautiful, damn hard, increasingly useful. That's fractals."_ -- Mandelbrot

