Mandelbrot Set
========================================================

- a _complex plain_ for which<br/>
$z_{n+1}\!= z_n^2 + c$
<br/>remains bounded
- named and defined by [Adrien Douady](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrien_Douady)
in tribute to [Benoit Mandelbrot](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benoit_Mandelbrot)
- the fractal was first drawn by Robert W. Brooks and Peter Matelski in 1978
<br/>`as ASCI art :)`

***

```{r, echo=FALSE, cache=TRUE}
source('mandelbrot.R')
image(mandelbrot(), col = c(grey(20:0 / 20)), asp = 1, axes = FALSE)
```

